reviewText: Jingle all the way was great, but deck the halls was more smarty and not family friendly.

Great BluRay double feature!  We watch these flicks every Christmas and to find them both together was a real treat!  Arnold Schwarzenegger and Sinbad in Jingle all the Way...classic!  And who would've seen Danny DeVito and Matthew Broderick in a Christmas movie together?  Deck the Halls may not be on everyone's "to watch" list at Christmastime but it has certainly made it's way onto ours.
